{"tid":1187101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明啊...","createTime":"2019-06-05T11:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T23:42:26.000Z","uid":149405,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b014baeeb764d794fe6654e47c1ed31524049a58","tid":1187101,"uid":149405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"我唔明，<br />\n<br />\n我有錢，算係富二代，生活唔洗憂。<br />\n<br />\n我樣中上，唔會話樣樣衰衰。<br />\n<br />\n我對你好，無去識其他人。<br />\n<br />\n我喜歡你成年。<br />\n<br />\n點解？點解你仲係唔肯接受我？<br />\n<br />\n點解我做咁多野，你都只係hea覆我？<br />\n<br />\n憑乜野佢又窮又爛玩又濫你鐘意佢？<br />\n<br />\n而我有錢佢佢專一過佢淨係愛你，<br />\n<br />\n只係換黎一句：對唔住<br />\n<br />\n我唔明啊。"},{"pid":"5cafc766a2d0694ca68e4f9d16a843b5dc1557f0","tid":1187101,"uid":128953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"b8e6610de45a03692409fe068e6fdf196a1c21f9","tid":1187101,"uid":149405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cafc766a2d0694ca68e4f9d16a843b5dc1557f0","tid":1187101,"uid":128953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"點解連你都要hea覆我？"},{"pid":"b156d839a3d0193234648ba1195d3e605da865b1","tid":1187101,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T12:12:26.000Z","msg":"👌"},{"pid":"7782d11a5eb8c87b20bc0603a86c93617ad11a6f","tid":1187101,"uid":211851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"首先有錢有樣唔係大哂，第二唔代表你中意人成年人地就中意你，感情永遠唔可以攞任何野黎衡量同比較。"},{"pid":"608ac56e7b5be9607cad61b402fb0328931bec79","tid":1187101,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"bbe492c6b209795cc7cda5cc14fc90def2f29ba9","tid":1187101,"uid":229959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T19:33:11.000Z","msg":"咁唔鍾意就唔鍾意㗎啦 冇得勉強個喎"},{"pid":"f773aa5d25c662b62d9bea803aaa132e847c99dd","tid":1187101,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T23:42:26.000Z","msg":"因為你鐘意你自己多過佢鐘意你。"}]}